OL,3,CMotorcyclist found lying in road after
OL,4,Csuspected hit-and-run
OL,6,FA motorcyclist has been seriously
OL,7,Finjured in a suspected hit-and-run.
OL,9,FThe man, in his 20s, was riding a
OL,10,Fblack motorbike on Sunderland Road in
OL,11,FFelling, Gateshead, when he was struck
OL,12,Fby a car and was reported to be lying
OL,13,Fin the road shortly before 2.55pm on
OL,14,FMonday (10 November), police said.
OL,16,FIt is believed the man had been
OL,17,Ftravelling from Stoneygate Lane
OL,18,Ftowards Sunderland Road when he was
OL,19,Fstruck by a vehicle.
