OL,3,CMotorcyclist found lying in road after
OL,4,Csuspected hit-and-run
OL,6,FHe was taken by ambulance to the Royal
OL,7,FVictoria Infirmary (RVI) in Newcastle
OL,8,Fwith serious injuries and remains
OL,9,Fthere in a critical but stable
OL,10,Fcondition.
OL,12,FNorthumbria Police said the driver
OL,13,Finvolved left the scene before
OL,14,Fofficers arrived. The force is now
OL,15,Fappealing for the driver to come
OL,16,Fforward.
