OL,3,CMotorcyclist found lying in road after
OL,4,Csuspected hit-and-run
OL,6,FSergeant Ben Rutherford, of
OL,7,FNorthumbria Police, said: "A man
OL,8,Fremains in hospital with serious
OL,9,Finjuries as a result of this incident
OL,10,F` while the driver involved remains
OL,11,Funknown.
OL,13,F"A number of enquiries remain underway
OL,14,Fto trace them, and we'd urge the
OL,15,Fperson responsible to do the right
OL,16,Fthing and come forward to police as
OL,17,Fsoon as possible. While our
OL,18,Finvestigation is still at an early
OL,19,Fstage and we are keeping an open mind,
OL,20,Fwe believe the car involved could be a
OL,21,FSEAT Cupra.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
