OL,3,CMotorcyclist found lying in road after
OL,4,Csuspected hit-and-run
OL,6,F"Any details, no matter how small they
OL,7,Fmay seem, could greatly help us."
OL,9,FA section of Sunderland Road was
OL,10,Fcordoned off by police for around five
OL,11,Fhours while they carried out
OL,12,Finvestigations. There was around five
OL,13,Fpolice cars in the area as well as a
OL,14,FForensic Collision Investigation Unit.
OL,16,FAn ambulance and a rapid response
OL,17,Fvehicle were also at the scene. The
OL,18,FNorth East Ambulance Service (NEAS)
OL,19,Fsaid they were called to the road
OL,20,Ftraffic incident at 2.52pm.
