OL,6,FA spokesperson for the service said:
OL,7,F"We dispatched one ambulance crew and
OL,8,Fa specialist paramedic to the
OL,9,Fincident. One patient was taken to the
OL,10,FRoyal Victoria Infirmary for further
OL,11,Ftreatment.
OL,13,FNorthumbria Police is keen to hear
OL,14,Ffrom witnesses who saw what happened
OL,15,For saw the rider and vehicle described
OL,16,Fin the area, and anyone who may have
OL,17,FCCTV or dashcam footage.
OL,19,FContact 101 with information.
